Name: C_SunSpec_ID
Description: Value = "SunS" (0x53756e53).  Uniquely identifies this as a SunSpec MODBUS Map

Name: C_SunSpec_DID_Common
Description: Value = 0x0001.  Uniquely identifies this as a SunSpec Common Model Block

Name: C_SunSpec_DID
Description: 101 = single phase; 102 = split phase1; 103 = three phase

Name: I_AC_VoltageAN
Description: AC Voltage Phase A to N value

Name: I_AC_VoltageBN
Description: AC Voltage Phase B to N value

Name: I_AC_VoltageCN
Description: AC Voltage Phase C to N value

Name: I_Status_Vendor
Description: Vendor-defined operating state and error codes. For error description, meaning and troubleshooting, refer to the SolarEdge Installation Guide.
